sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Primary as Primary DB
    participant WAL as Write-Ahead Log
    participant Replica as Replica DB
    participant StandbyWAL as Standby WAL

    Client->>Primary: Write transaction
    Primary->>WAL: Append log entry (LSN 1042)
    WAL-->>Primary: Logged
    Primary->>Primary: Apply change to storage
    Primary->>Replica: Ship WAL segment (LSN 1042)
    Replica->>StandbyWAL: Write received segment
    StandbyWAL-->>Replica: Written
    Replica->>Replica: Apply change to storage
    Replica-->>Primary: Ack LSN 1042
    Primary-->>Client: Write confirmed
    Note over Primary,Replica: Replication lag = 0 (synchronous mode)
